The two systems FFS2 and 3G3 use different methods of determining range,
3G3 using the Aiming Range Class(RC) to determine the T4 range catagory ie
RC   T4 Range
1    Contact(3m)
2    Very Short(15m)
3    Short(45m)
4    Medium(150m)
5    Long(450m)
6    Very Long(1.5km)
7    Ext Long(3km)
8    Sub-Regional(10km)

In 3G3 there is no aiming RC above 8. 
