 8           500 km   5.0E+05     7m30s      5m20s    4m20s    3m50s      3m20s     3m        2m20s     1m40s 
 9         5,000 km   5.0E+06     24m       17m      14m       12m       11m        9m40s     7m30s     5m20s 
